                  <h2>Stress Symptoms</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Look out for extreme cases of the following if you feel the work's piling up:</p>
                <ul class="my_list">
                  <li>Difficulty getting to sleep or difficulty waking up in the morning</li>
                  <li>Constant tiredness</li>
                  <li>Forgetfulness</li>
                  <li>Unexplained aches and pains</li>
                  <li>Poor appetite</li>
                  <li>Loss of interest in activities</li>
                  <li>Increased anxiety and irritability</li>
                  <li>Increased heart rate</li>
                  <li>Migraines/headaches</li>
                  <li>Blurred vision</li>
                  <li>Dizziness</li>
                </ul>
                <p>If you've noticed three or more of the above symptoms and you've experienced them for a few weeks you
                  may need to do something about your stress levels.</p>
              </div>
